Enum FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum

    public enum FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum
extends java.lang.Enum<FeatureEditUpdateTypeEnum>
    Types of screen operations performed by the user when Map is in EDIT_MODE or DRAW_MODE EditorMode. The context for these operations is either FeatureEditEvent or FeatureEditEvent
